OL,3,CEndometriosis patient campaigns for
OL,4,CJess's rule in Wales
OL,6,FCampaigners are calling on the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment to implement a 'three-
OL,8,Fstrike rule' to encourage GPs to
OL,9,Frethink a primary diagnosis if a
OL,10,Fpatient presents three times with the
OL,11,Fsame symptoms.
OL,13,FTiffany Summerfield, 32, from Cardiff,
OL,14,Fwas diagnosed with endometriosis at 19
OL,15,Fafter she collapsed during her period.
OL,16,FIn the years since, she has endured
OL,17,Ffive surgeries to try and relieve the
OL,18,Fchronic pain that has come to define
OL,19,Fher adult life.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1772223642
OL,3,CEndometriosis patient campaigns for
OL,4,CJess's rule in Wales
OL,6,FThe proposed measure, known as 'Jess's
OL,7,FRule,' requires a diagnostic rethink
OL,8,Fafter three consultations for the same
OL,9,Fissue. While the rule is currently
OL,10,Fbeing implemented in NHS England, it
OL,11,Fhas not yet been adopted in Wales.
OL,13,F"It is all too common in women's
OL,14,Fhealth for symptoms to be dismissed,"
OL,15,FTiffany said. "They say, 'try the
OL,16,Fpill' or 'try this and that first,'
OL,17,Fbut a lot of the time it is actually
OL,18,Fmasking symptoms rather than getting
OL,19,Fto the root cause of what is going
OL,20,Fon...
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1772223642
OL,3,CEndometriosis patient campaigns for
OL,4,CJess's rule in Wales
OL,6,F"Knowing that after three visits the
OL,7,FGP would have to legally explore
OL,8,Fdifferent referrals and avenues,
OL,9,Factually thinking about what is
OL,10,Fcausing the issue, would stop people
OL,11,Fspending years being dismissed."
OL,13,FTiffany has since launched a Senedd
OL,14,Fpetition calling on the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment to implement the change. If
OL,16,Fthe petition receives over 10,000
OL,17,Fsignatures, the Petitions Committee
OL,18,Fwill consider it for a full debate in
OL,19,Fthe Senedd chamber.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
