PN,46104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1772223642
OL,3,CEndometriosis patient campaigns for
OL,4,CJess's rule in Wales
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government said:
OL,7,F"Endometriosis and adenomyosis are
OL,8,Fpriority areas in our Women's Health
OL,9,FPlan, and we are working to ensure
OL,10,Fsymptoms are recognised and acted on
OL,11,Fsooner.
OL,13,F"We have funded a specialist
OL,14,Fendometriosis nurse in every health
OL,15,Fboard, created the Endometriosis Cymru
OL,16,Fwebsite, and provided #50m to help
OL,17,Freduce the longest waiting times,
OL,18,Fincluding for gynaecology. We are also
OL,19,Fraising awareness among GPs and have
OL,20,Fintroduced dedicated training for NHS
OL,21,Fstaff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1772223642
OL,3,CEndometriosis patient campaigns for
OL,4,CJess's rule in Wales
OL,6,F"A further #3m is supporting the
OL,7,Fdelivery of the plan, which includes
OL,8,Festablishing a Women's Health Hub in
OL,9,Fevery health board by March 2026."
OL,11,FJessica Brady passed away in December
OL,12,F2020 at the age of just 27, after it
OL,13,Fwas discovered she had stage four
OL,14,Fcancer.
OL,16,FIn the five months leading up to her
OL,17,Fdeath, Jess had 20 consultations with
OL,18,Fher GP practice, yet her cancer
OL,19,Fremained undiagnosed. Following her
OL,20,Fdeath, her family launched a campaign
OL,21,Ffor "Jess's Rule."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1772223642
OL,3,CEndometriosis patient campaigns for
OL,4,CJess's rule in Wales
OL,6,FThe proposed measure would require a
OL,7,Fsenior clinician to review a patient's
OL,8,Fcase if they have sought help three
OL,9,Ftimes for the same symptoms without a
OL,10,Fdiagnosis.
OL,12,FJess's mother, Andrea Brady, said it
OL,13,Fis "hugely" important to get Jess's
OL,14,FRule implemented in Wales.
OL,16,F"It's not a complicated sort of
OL,17,Finitiative, and it really could save
OL,18,Flives," she said. "We have been
OL,19,Fapproached as a charity from as far
OL,20,Fafield as New Zealand.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1772223642
OL,3,CEndometriosis patient campaigns for
OL,4,CJess's rule in Wales
OL,6,F"I give my absolute, wholehearted
OL,7,Fsupport for the initiative being taken
OL,8,Fup in Wales."
OL,10,FDr. Rowena Christmas, Chair of RCGP
OL,11,FCymru Wales, welcomed the call to
OL,12,Fadopt the principles of Jess's Rule.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1772223642
OL,3,CEndometriosis patient campaigns for
OL,4,CJess's rule in Wales
OL,6,F"It is a core part of our jobs as GPs
OL,7,Fto always look for warning signs of
OL,8,Fserious illness," Dr. Christmas said.
OL,9,F"The value in Jess's Rule is that it
OL,10,Fformalises 'best practice' in general
OL,11,Fpractice, with its focus on the
OL,12,Fimportance of taking the time to
OL,13,Freflect and review a diagnosis if a
OL,14,Ftreatment does not seem to be working
OL,15,Fas expected.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1772223642
OL,3,CEndometriosis patient campaigns for
OL,4,CJess's rule in Wales
OL,6,F"Prompt diagnosis results in better
OL,7,Foutcomes for patients, but many
OL,8,Fserious conditions`including many
OL,9,Fcancers`are challenging to identify in
OL,10,Fprimary care because symptoms are
OL,11,Foften similar to less serious, more
OL,12,Fcommon conditions."
OL,14,FDr. Christmas added that while
OL,15,F"workforce shortages and workload
OL,16,Fpressures" must be addressed to
OL,17,Fimprove continuity of care, the rule
OL,18,Fwould be a significant step forward.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/9
